title: vivo Y73 (Diamond Flare, 128 GB)  (8 GB RAM)

product_specification.In The Box: Handset, Earphones, USB Cable Type C, USB Power Adapter, SIM Ejector, Protective Case, Protective Film Applied, Documentation
product_specification.Other Display Features: 20:09 Aspect Ratio, 90.37% Screen-to-body Ratio, Ultra Slim AG Glass
product_specification.Primary Camera Features: Triple Rear Camera Setup: 64MP Main Camera (f/1.79 Aperture, AF) + 2MP Bokeh Camera (f/2.4 Aperture) + 2MP Macro (f/2.4 Aperture), Features: 4K Video, Eye Autofocus, Night, Ultra Stable Video, Super Macro, Bokeh Portrait, Multi-Style Portrait, High Resolution, PANO, Live Photo, Slo-Mo, Time Lapse, PRO, DOC, AR Stickers
product_specification.Secondary Camera Features: 16MP Front Camera, f/2.0 Aperture, Camera Features: Night, Steadiface, Portrait Light Effect, Video Face Beauty, Dual-View Video
product_specification.Sensors: Accelerometer, Ambient Light Sensor, Proximity Sensor, E-compass, Fingerprint Sensor (In-Display), Gyroscope (Entity)
product_specification.Other Features: Widevine L1 Certified, App Clone, 33W Flashcharge (11V/3A), 12nm Processor
product_specification.Audio Formats: WAV, MP3, MP2, MIDI, Vorbis, APE, FLAC
product_specification.Warranty Summary: 1 Year for Handset and 6 Months for In-box Accessories

product_description.7.38 mm AG Glass: The Vivo Y73 is a stylish smartphone featuring a 7.38 mm sleek design. Along with an AG Matte Glass finish surface, it offers a delicate yet premium touch. The rounded frame further offers a relaxed and comfortable grip.
product_description.64 MP Ultra HD Photos: The powerful 64 MP Ultra HD main camera lets you capture the stunning beauty of your surroundings with all its glory.
product_description.AI Super Night Mode: This smartphone features upgraded algorithms and an AI-supported noise reduction technology to click rich and clear night shots. Using this mode, you can capture the magnificent moments of the night.
product_description.33 W FlashCharge: The Vivo Y73 comes with a 4000 mAh battery to ensure that you do not have to carry your charger everywhere. Also, its 33 W FlashCharge feature boosts the battery life by up to 64% with about 30 minutes of charging.
product_description.8 GB RAM + 3 GB Extended RAM: The 8 GB of RAM of this smartphone is empowered by Extended RAM technology to offer you a high-speed and smooth 8 GB + 3 GB experience with a tap on the 3 GB of external storage space. So, you can access up to 20 apps simultaneously.
product_description.16.35 cm (6.44) AMOLED Display: This smartphone comes with a 16.35 cm (6.44) FHD+ AMOLED display. Thus, the 2400 x 1080 resolution offers rich, detailed, and true-to-life visuals.
product_description.Dual-view Video: With this feature, you can roll the front and rear cameras simultaneously to capture both sides of your surroundings.
product_description.Funtouch OS 11.1: This Vivo smartphone runs on the Funtouch OS 11.1 that is based on Android 11 and features a minimalist and user-friendly interface. Thus, this smartphone offers an impressive mobile computing experience.
